maximum objectives, but they see that as the best of the possible outcomes or at least the least

49:50.880 --> 50:04.000
worse. That's the nature of diplomatic settlements. If you don't want that, let's escalate to total

50:04.000 --> 50:13.920
destruction. Yeah. We've about 10 minutes left. I'm going to come to a couple of questions from

