58:38.800 --> 58:43.120
Too much goes on in the world to know everything. But what you're interested in,

58:43.120 --> 58:49.200
you think are important pursuers. But don't get caught up in self-reinforcing bubbles.

58:49.920 --> 58:56.880
And assume that what the major media are presenting is an accurate picture of the world.

58:57.600 --> 59:04.960
