to concentrated power in the private system and in the state system, which are closely related,

59:12.800 --> 59:18.880
of course, in state-connected societies. So understand the nature of the institutions

59:18.880 --> 59:26.560
and take a careful look with a critical eye. Recognize that we're fine journalists,

59:26.560 --> 59:30.160
trustworthy, and so on. That's the way it can proceed.

